    "Subsequently, we explore potential correlations between processes induced by the b → sℓ - 1 ℓ + 2 transition and purely leptonic LFV modes.",
    "3The plan of the paper is as follows: In Sec.",
    "2 we describe the main features of the ABCD model, summarising the discussion in [1].",
    "3 we select the set of observables to study within the model, and identify the correlations among them to investigate.",
    "The results of the numerical analysis are presented in Sec. 4."
